main event: A person reported seeing a green aircraft-like object moving at a moderate speed with no visible means of propulsion over Manchester, New Hampshire on October 26, 1968.
interesting points: The object appeared to be about the size of a small private plane and was very quiet.
The witness noticed an unusual sound that was loud and rapidly fading.
The object moved from west to east at a gradual inclination before disappearing over the horizon.
The witness was not wearing glasses at the time of the sighting.
There was no physical evidence left behind by the phenomenon.
photographs: yes, the report includes a photograph of the object
